$ Avaloq: Business Units

{ MESI: Public and private business units

  With MESI (Multi entity single instance) activated, Avaloq has a public and several private BUs.

  Data within the public BU is visible to all other BUs while private BU data is visible to the respective
  BU only.

}
{ Determining the current session BU

code {
select session#.session#bu_id from dual;
code }

}
